    • Class it.polimi.sw.GC50.model.cards.PlayableCard

      class PlayableCard extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • bonus
          Bonus bonus
          Represents the condition regarding the player's score increment obtained when placing the card, computed as points * bonus.checkBonus(...)
        • code
          String code
        • color
          Color color
        • corners
          Corner[] corners
          Represents the corners of the card (always initialized as an array of length 4) In order, it contains the SW, NW, NE and SE corners
        • fixedResources
          List<Resource> fixedResources
          Represents the list of resources present in the center of the card
        • points
          int points
          Represents the number at the top of the card (not necessarily the score obtained by the player when placing it)
